    "Mark as finished and take a post-study questionnaire: When both you and the other player are done designing the object, you will mark the study as complete (using a provided option) and take a post-study questionnaire.",
    "Note that you may not always reach an agreement with the other participant.",
    "But when you are done, you should still mark the task as finished and take the post-study questionnaire. b.",
    "You should plan to spend 15-20 minutes on the questionnaire.",
    "The conversations should only focus on object design."
